.com/story/suburbarazzi/2014/06/17/movie-starring-tina-fey-amy-poehler-filming-haverstraw/10673615/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有人發現費和寶拉在{{tsl|en|Pearl River, New York||珍珠河}}（Pearl River）拍攝<ref>{{cite news|last1=RANKIN|first1=PMSEIJA|title=Here's The First Look At Tina & Amy's New Movie|url=http://www.refinery29.com/2014/06/69865/tina-fey-amy-poehler-movie-pictures|accessdate=July 7, 2014|publisher=refinery29.com|date=June 19, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303235821/http://www.refinery29.com/2014/06/69865/tina-fey-amy-poehler-movie-pictures|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月24日，拍攝場景則於{{tsl|en|Five Towns College||五鎮學院}}和{{tsl|en|Dix Hills, New York||迪克斯山}}附近<ref>{{cite news|title=The Nest is filming around Five Towns College|url=https://twitter.com/olv/status/481490755509170177|accessdate=July 1, 2014|publisher=twitter.com|date=June 24, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304231249/https://twitter.com/olv/status/481490755509170177|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月22日，也在{{tsl|en|Huntington, New York||杭丁頓}}附近的喬恩．麥加利斯Jon Megaris髮廊進行拍攝<ref>{{cite news|title=Tina Fey, Amy Poehler film 'Sisters' at Huntington hair salon|url=http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/movies/tina-fey-amy-poehler-film-sisters-at-huntington-hair-salon-1.9833607|accessdate=January 22, 2015|publisher=Newsday|date=January 22, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307143256/http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/movies/tina-fey-amy-poehler-film-sisters-at-huntington-hair-salon-1.9833607|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
